        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2863165853" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8858390460783773600">This is a really interesting series of short travelogues written in the 1990s. I found the trips through Eastern Europe most absorbing. The chapter on England illustrated how the ordination of women lead many Christians to convert to Catholicism. I think he missed the fact that many Catholics started to leave and move across to the Church of England for the same reason. </span>

          </span>
