        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1540324313" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12144729795707787289">I thoroughly enjoyed Colm Tóibín&apos;s travel book cum memoir about Catholic Europe, partly because I&apos;ve visited many of the places he did and also, having been brought up in the Catholic Church myself, it was fascinating to read about how the Church is viewed within its different, and often diverse, cultures and communities. It also gives fascinating glimpses into the history of many European countries, in particular of the emerging Eastern European democracies, as they were in the 1990s when he wr</span>
  <span id="freeText12144729795707787289" style="display:none">I thoroughly enjoyed Colm Tóibín's travel book cum memoir about Catholic Europe, partly because I've visited many of the places he did and also, having been brought up in the Catholic Church myself, it was fascinating to read about how the Church is viewed within its different, and often diverse, cultures and communities. It also gives fascinating glimpses into the history of many European countries, in particular of the emerging Eastern European democracies, as they were in the 1990s when he wrote the book. It is an intense, and dense, read for such a slim-looking book and hard to read in one sitting, as there is so much information to digest and reflect upon.</span>
  <a data-text-id="12144729795707787289" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


